<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf0099837-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7422"><num value="7422">§ 7422.</num><heading> Amendments to orders</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this subchapter applicable to an order shall be applicable to any amendment to an order, except that <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s7417">section 7417 of this title</ref> shall not apply to an amendment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf0099838-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tV/s523">Pub. L. 104–127, title V, § 523</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1047">110 Stat. 1047</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
